name: Dark Cosmic Erasure Jhin
description: Jhin was an interstellar entity, consumed by the Dark Star and given new purpose. Now his ageless mind is infected by visions of omnipotence, and consumed by an insatiable hunger. He scours entire regions of space seemingly on a whim, using the remnants to create bizarre, silent objets d'art.

wikiSkinData.distribution: 1% drop rate from Cosmic 2023 Capsules or opening 30 Cosmic 2023 Capsules
